# Copy this file to .env for local `netlify dev`, and/or set the same
# names under Site configuration -> Environment variables in the Netlify
# dashboard for production.
#
# When these are set, the Stackby Cloud Storage Setup panel in the app
# becomes optional — the Netlify Function will use these instead, so the
# API key never has to be typed into the browser or stored in localStorage.

